entries.femaleVariant: All right, I'm in position. I have you in range.
The sniper is no longer a problem. Keep moving.
Careful. There's a sniper perched in the tower.
Dammit! Stay out of sight!
Keep your eyes peeled. I see several heavy hitters.
OK, you're near the main structure. That has to be where they're holding Saul.
OK, main building. Watch for vermin.
Ugh... Panam... Got a girl here... Dead.
entries.maleVariant: Oh, Panam... Got a girl here... Dead.

entries.femaleVariant: Any progress? Is he singing yet?
Rottin' in the basement a while longer oughta loosen his pipes.
'Ey? Shouldn't you be downstairs?
I was. I had to feed the mangy mutt.
I wanna see him up close.
Panam! Found Saul, I think. Locked in the cellar.
entries.maleVariant: Panam! I found Saul, I think. Locked in the cellar.

entries.femaleVariant: How is he?
Saul is somewhere inside. I feel it in my bones.
Made it to the cellar. If they're holdin' him anywhere, it's here.
On our way out now!
I'm firing up the engine! I'll be right there!
Think I found a sneaky way to slip in…
Perfect. These brutes will never be the wiser.
Dammit, V! So much for being sly!
Knowing them, they have something important in there. You might even gain access to the security system.
Keep your head down and plow straight ahead!
From there, you can access a footbridge leading to the main structure.
Dammit!
Disemboweled… and not just for her chrome, I don't think.
Fucking Raffens! Soulless filth! There's no line they won't cross, none!
Keep looking, V. Maybe... just maybe we're not too late.
Find Saul and you two get out of there!
Pulled off his gag and you know what the bastard did? Nearly bit off my fingers!
He still have his teeth? You know, he doesn't really need those to talk.
Huh... Yeah, I'll have to remember that next time.
Now that you mention it, he doesn't need his eyes, either.
Fuckin' hell, sure hope so'... It's takin' too long.
A good way to get to the garage.
That should be their garage. It's heavily guarded.
Remember what I told you. Find the control room and you'll gain access to the security cams.
Just wait. Nothing to see just yet.
Nah, it's hard to say. Too dark.
entries.maleVariant: Pff, it's hard to say. Too dark.

entries.femaleVariant: OK, get down there and get him. Maybe we made it in time.
Wait'll they give 'im a taste of the torch, try to melt him down.
Dammit, dammit, dammit!
Fuck, let's finish this! Do your thing!
Been here before, y'know.
Good. You survived once, so let's go for two.
Ugh, found something…
